IMDB Top 250 Movies Analysis
This project involves analyzing IMDb data to retrieve the top 250 movies based on their ratings. The analysis was performed using Python and pandas, and the data was analyzed in a Jupyter Notebook.

Project Overview
The main objectives of this project are:
1. Load IMDb data from TSV (Tab-Separated Values) files.
2. Merge the datasets to create a comprehensive DataFrame containing movie details and their ratings.
3. Filter the dataset to include only movies.
4. Sort the movies based on their average ratings and number of votes.
5. Retrieve and display the top 250 movies.
